Of the Internet users in MENA (71 percent of the region), 94 percent spend at least 2 hours a day on social media, signalling that Internet usage has become nearly synonymous with social media usage. Among Internet users, a substantial portion (45 percent) are heavy social media users (spending 5 hours and above).

